Nested Class Summary
static class QVWebServiceException.ErrorCode
          ErrorCode is the machine-parsable code for the exception AUTH_ERROR = authentication error (incorrect QVCredentials) MISSING_REQUIRED_DATA = the data in the request was missing required fields (error message will elaborate) DATA_INVALID = the data in the request contained invalid fields (error message will elaborate) NOT_VERIFIED = the sender's mobile number has not been verified APP_FAULT = application error on our side (io, db, etc)
